3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The problem involves optimizing the agents' navigation to visit critical locations as quickly as possible, which is a common theme in AI research.
4. cs.RO (Robotics) - The problem involves navigating through an environment, which is a common theme in robotics research.
5. cs.CG (Computational Geometry) - The paper discusses the topology of the environment and how it affects the computational complexity of the problem, which is a common theme in computational geometry research.
